==英老兵致謝==
2012年9月16日[[英國|英國]][[二戰|二戰]]英緬第一師老兵杰拉德·費茲派翠克（Gerald Fitzpatrick<ref>[http://www.geraldfitzpatrick.co.uk/p/biography.html?m=1 Biography] {{Wayback|url=http://www.geraldfitzpatrick.co.uk/p/biography.html?m=1 |date=20190609223716 }}Gerald Fitzpatrick.co.uk，2019年</ref>）首度造訪[[美國|美國]]，向當時領導中國遠征軍113團團長劉放吾的長女劉偉華、次子劉偉民，當面致謝<ref name="worldjournal-20186180">{{cite news|url=http://www.worldjournal.com/view/full_news/20186180/article-%E4%BB%81%E5%AE%89%E7%BE%8C%E5%A4%A7%E6%8D%B7-%E8%8B%B1%E8%80%81%E5%85%B5%E8%AC%9D%E6%81%A9?instance=top_rec|title=仁安羌大捷 英老兵謝恩|publisher=世界日報|accessdate=2012-09-21|archive-date=2012-10-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121023020423/http://worldjournal.com/view/full_news/20186180/article-%E4%BB%81%E5%AE%89%E7%BE%8C%E5%A4%A7%E6%8D%B7-%E8%8B%B1%E8%80%81%E5%85%B5%E8%AC%9D%E6%81%A9?instance=top_rec|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref name="president-gov-tw-29516"/>。費茲派翠克在2000年寫成《No Mandalay, No Maymyo (79 Survive)》一書<ref>{{cite book|author=Gerald Fitzpatrick|title=''No Mandalay, No Maymyo (79 Survive): Unique Episodes in British History''|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=1aawAAAAIAAJ|year=2001|publisher=Book Guild|isbn=978-1-85776-520-5}}</ref><ref name="president-gov-tw-29516"/>，2012年5月再出 《Ditched in Burma》一書<ref>[http://www.amazon.co.uk/Ditched-Burma-Mandalay-Maymyo-Survive/dp/0957278306 Ditched in Burma: No Mandalay, No Maymyo, 79 Survive] {{Wayback|url=http://www.amazon.co.uk/Ditched-Burma-Mandalay-Maymyo-Survive/dp/0957278306 |date=20190629042455 }}，ISBN  978-0957278301</ref>。<ref name="worldjournal-20186180"/><ref name="president-gov-tw-29516"/>記錄被二戰英緬軍總司令[[哈羅德·亞歷山大，第一代突尼斯的亞歷山大伯爵|亞歷山大]]刻意隱瞞的戰況真相。中華民國駐美代表處軍事代表團團長黎賢聖少將，17日也以一面中華民國國防部建國百年紀念牌贈與費茲派翠克，感謝他著書還原仁安羌戰役歷史真相。<ref name="worldjournal-20186180"/><ref name="president-gov-tw-29516"/>2013年3月27日，馬英九總統上午接見英國退役陸軍上尉費茲派翠克（Gerald Fitzpatrick）伉儷，其第三本著作《Chinese Saves Brits in Burma》<ref>[http://www.amazon.com/Chinese-Save-Brits-Battle-Yenangyaung/dp/0957278314/ref=sr_1_10?s=books&ie=UTF8&qid=1411576818&sr=1-10 Chinese Save Brits - in Burma: (Battle of Yenangyaung)]，ISBN 978-0957278318 ; [http://www.amazon.com/Chinese-Save-Brits-Battle-Yenangyaung-ebook/dp/B00HSOWN8S Kindle Edition] {{Wayback|url=http://www.amazon.com/Chinese-Save-Brits-Battle-Yenangyaung-ebook/dp/B00HSOWN8S |date=20170324173819 }}</ref>也已面世。<ref name="president-gov-tw-29516">[http://www.president.gov.tw/Default.aspx?tabid=131&itemid=29516 總統接見英國退役陸軍上尉費茲派翠克（Gerald Fitzpatrick）伉儷] {{Wayback|url=http://www.president.gov.tw/Default.aspx?tabid=131&itemid=29516 |date=20170911024106 }} - 中華民國102年03月27日</ref>

